{"id": "26606", "post": "<div class=\"post-26606 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-alma-linux tag-centos tag-distro tag-ibm tag-linux tag-red-hat tag-rocky-linux\" id=\"post-26606\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-results-what-are-your-centos-plans/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Poll Results: What are Your CentOS Plans?</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/alma-linux/\" rel=\"tag\">alma linux</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/centos/\" rel=\"tag\">centos</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/distro/\" rel=\"tag\">distro</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ibm/\" rel=\"tag\">ibm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/linux/\" rel=\"tag\">linux</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/red-hat/\" rel=\"tag\">red hat</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/rocky-linux/\" rel=\"tag\">rocky linux</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> March 25, 2021 @ 12:00 am, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p>We recently asked you what your <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-what-are-your-centos-plans/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">plans were regarding CentOS</a>.&nbsp; As you may have read, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/centos-rip-long-live-centos-stream/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CentOS is changing</a> and we were curious how the community was going to react.</p><p>The results are in!&nbsp; With 270 votes, here are the raw results:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-26607 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"320\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll.png 700w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll-300x234.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll.png 700w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll-300x234.png.webp 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p>You\u2019ll notice that almost 30% of respondents don\u2019t use CentOS and don\u2019t plan on using it in the future.&nbsp; If we exclude them to focus just on CentOS people, here are the results:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26608 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"336\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2.png.webp 700w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2-300x144.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2.png.webp 700w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/centos_poll2-300x144.png.webp 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p>Interesting!&nbsp; About a third of CentOS users are planning to abandon the distro.&nbsp; Of those who are sticking with it, 23% are sticking with CentOS regardless of the changes and 13% will move to RHEL.&nbsp; 30% of users will move to either Alma or Rocky Linux.&nbsp; Only 5% are moving to a completely different distro.</p><p>Thanks for the insight, folks!</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/libreplanet-fsf-conference-is-free-and-one-week-from-today/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LibrePlanet (the FSF Conference) One Week From Today - and it's Free (as in Beer)!\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/libre_planet_logo-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">LibrePlanet (the FSF Conference) One Week From Today - and it's Free (as in Beer)!</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-what-are-your-centos-plans/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Poll: What are Your CentOS Plans?\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lowendbox-poll-150x150.jpg) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Poll: What are Your CentOS Plans?</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/how-to-fire-up-wordpress-in-three-commands/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"How to Fire Up WordPress in Three Commands\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wordpress-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">How to Fire Up WordPress in Three Commands</div></div></a